title: Derek Pritchard, Baron Pritchard
text:
Derek Wilbraham Pritchard, Baron Pritchard (8 June 1910 – 18 October 1995) was a British businessman and life peer.
Biography.
Pritchard was <a href="knight">knight</a>ed in 1968 and created a life peer, as <a href="Baron">Baron</a> Pritchard, of <a href="West%20Haddon">West Haddon</a> in Northamptonshire on 30 January 1975.
